Project_Title: SHED aggregate-derived exosomes promote angiogenesis in pulp regeneration
Project_Description: miRNA microarray analyses were performed on SHED aggregate and SHED cells. SHED-Exo represented exosomes derived from SHED cells, SHED_A-EXO represented exosomes derived from SHED aggregate, and SHED-EXO was the control group of SHED_A-EXO.
